          <li>added undo, redo, close app and close active window shortcuts</li>
          <li>added current file as title, with unsaved changes indicator</li>
          <li>improved background rendering</li>
          <li>UI tweaks</li>
          <li>bug fixes</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
