          <li>new and improved gestures and shortcuts (zoom with "ctrl+scroll", drag the canvas with the middle mouse button)</li>
          <li>improved strokes algorithms</li>
          <li>bug fixes</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.1.3" date="2021-10-08">
